{"tid":1665921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"換妝離場真係好重要好重要好重要架！","createTime":"2019-10-20T17:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T18:11:10.000Z","uid":55937,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0129e8a3bb0212fff03470bd9dbba70874a12e5e","tid":1665921,"uid":55937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:58:03.000Z","msg":"已經唔係一兩次既事，所以先開post講講。<br />\n每次發夢見到d年紀輕既手足離場果時唔換衫，<br />\n行埋去同佢地如果走就換妝喇，一係話冇帶衫，一係話換左，<br />\n但係由黑色衫換左另一件黑色衫係有咩作用呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足們，求下你地保護自己，唔係點係煲底相見呀我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要做到不受傷就帶Gear又眼罩又豬咀又遮etc，<br />\n要做到不被捕，離場換妝都係好重要好重要好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係帶多件非黑色衫換咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家d狗仲要係住宅區 / 黨鐵站守株待兔，全黑咁搭車走係咪搏拉呀&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b597253399461df97f7b31751c9292f9040434f9","tid":1665921,"uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:58:54.000Z","msg":"黑衫換黑衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2445e03e73f187ad548faf73f7260bca986affb","tid":1665921,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:59:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1</a><br />\n[文宣升級] 郵差叔叔送信純熟將文宣迅速送出!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4H03stW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4H03stW.png&h=37a4782b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"559489c0a5acb6d8e66cce7215c6f01718dc9d87","tid":1665921,"uid":238613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b597253399461df97f7b31751c9292f9040434f9","tid":1665921,"uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:58:54.000Z","msg":"黑衫換黑衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gi